room_title: Escape room "Agent Harper" by Lock'Em Up Escape Rooms in San Antonio
room_address: 12332 I-10 Frontage Rd, San Antonio, TX 78230
room_description:
Agent Harper has gone missing. He was working undercover in order to capture an international criminal known as Simeon. You and a group of other special agents must search through Agent Harper’s office in order to find clues that will lead us to Harper & Simeon.

You have 1 hour before Simeon leaves the country.

Will you succeed? Or will Simeon get away possibly forever…
